---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Abundant Air Conditioning & Heating LLC." path="/privacy">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink-soft">Effective date: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-ink-soft">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Abundant Air Conditioning &amp; Heating LLC is a family-run HVAC company based in La Quinta, CA. Our website is <a href="https://abundantairac.com" class="text-coral hover:underline">abundantairac.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">What information we collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We only collect information you voluntarily provide when you fill out a contact or service request form on this site. That includes:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Type of service needed</li>
          <li>Any message you write</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not collect payment information. There are no user accounts on this site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">How we use it</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">The information you submit is used only to respond to your service inquiry. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Form processing</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Our contact forms are processed by <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:underline">Web3Forms</a>, a third-party form service. When you submit a form, your data is transmitted through their service and delivered to our email inbox. Please review their privacy policy for details on how they handle form data.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">This site does not set its own cookies. Our hosting infrastructure uses Cloudflare, which may set technical cookies (prefixed <code class="rounded bg-sand px-1 text-sm">cf_</code>) for security and performance purposes. These cookies do not identify you personally. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-coral hover:underline">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a> for details.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Analytics</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not currently use any analytics or tracking tools on this site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Data security</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">This site is served over HTTPS. Form submissions travel through encrypted connections. We retain your contact information only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Contact us about privacy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">If you have questions about this policy or want to request deletion of your information, you can reach us at:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@abundantairac.com" class="text-coral hover:underline">info@abundantairac.com</a></li>
          <li>Phone: <a href="tel:7604233404" class="text-coral hover:underline">(760) 423-3404</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">If we make material changes to this policy, we will update the effective date above.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
